in custom component we can put ng-content
that use when we use custom component like

<div>
  <ng-content select=".head"></ng-content>
  <ng-content select=".body"></ng-content>  
</div>


to use this is custom component
<app-custom-component>
  <div class="head"></div>
  <div class="body" <div/>
<app-custom-component>
OR

ng-container : replace div

to use this is custom component
<app-custom-component>
  <ng-container class="head"></ng-container>
  <ng-container class="body" </ng-container> 
<app-custom-component>





















